00116 #define orxCOMMAND_REGISTER_CORE_COMMAND(MODULE, COMMAND, RESULT_NAME, RESULT_TYPE, REQ_PARAM_NUMBER, OPT_PARAM_NUMBER, ...)        \
00117 do                                                                                                                                  \
00118 {                                                                                                                                   \
00119   orxCOMMAND_VAR_DEF  stResult;                                                                                                     \
00120   orxCOMMAND_VAR_DEF  astParamList[REQ_PARAM_NUMBER + OPT_PARAM_NUMBER + 1] = {__VA_ARGS__};                                        \
00121   orxSTATUS           eStatus;                                                                                                      \
00122   stResult.eType  = RESULT_TYPE;                                                                                                    \
00123   stResult.zName  = RESULT_NAME;                                                                                                    \
00124   eStatus         = orxCommand_Register(#MODULE"."#COMMAND, orx##MODULE##_Command##COMMAND, REQ_PARAM_NUMBER, OPT_PARAM_NUMBER, astParamList, &stResult);\
00125   orxASSERT(eStatus != orxSTATUS_FAILURE);                                                                                          \
00126 } while(orxFALSE)

00128 #define orxCOMMAND_UNREGISTER_CORE_COMMAND(MODULE, COMMAND)                                                                         \
00129 do                                                                                                                                  \
00130 {                                                                                                                                   \
00131   orxCommand_Unregister(#MODULE"."#COMMAND);                                                                                        \
00132 } while(orxFALSE)
